Package: bestan
Title: Bayesian estimation for the t-test using Stan
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Matti", "Vuorre", , "mv2521@columbia.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package implements the model described in Kruschke, 2013:
"Bayesian Estimation Supersedes the t-test" JEP:G, 142(2), but uses Stan for MCMC sampling.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.2)
License: MIT license
LazyData: true
Imports:
    rstan,
    ggplot2,
    dplyr
